race.comment: FAMILY OF LEAGUE (1) resumes here but was in consistent form prior to the spell and does boast a win over this distance range. Gets 2kg off with the claim and can run a big race while fresh. ECHO HUNTER (6) has been thereabouts at the past few outings and will be rock-hard fit for this. Has to be included. LADY ZAYDI (3) has hit the top-five in 11 of her past 12 starts and rarely puts in a poor one. A must for the multiples. RESOLUTE LADY (4) was well in the betting at the latest effort and didn't let backers down with a solid Kilcoy victory. In the mix. BRODIES VOYAGE (5) rounds out the selections in a race with only a handful of chances.
